			<td class="tg-031e"><strong>hat</strong></td>
			<td align="center" class="tg-031e">140</td>
			<td align="center" class="tg-031e">0</td>
		</tr>
	</tbody>
</table>

<p> </p>
]]></question>
    <help/>
    <language><![CDATA[de]]></language>
    <script/>
   </row>
   <row>
    <id><![CDATA[504700]]></id>
    <qid><![CDATA[535795]]></qid>
    <question><![CDATA[<p> </p>

<p>Familie Müller benötigt 80 Quadratmeter und Familie Schneider 120 Quadratmeter.</p>

<p>In diesem Fall hat Familie Müller 160 Quadratmeter und Familie Schneider 90 Quadratmeter.</p>

<p>Bitte geben Sie unten an, wie <strong>gerecht</strong> Familie Müller hier versorgt ist.</p>

<p> </p>

<table border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1">
	<tbody>
		<tr>
			<th class="tg-031e"> </th>
			<th align="center" class="tg-031e">Familie Müller</th>
			<th align="center" class="tg-031e">Familie Schneider</th>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td class="tg-031e"><strong>benötigt</strong></td>
			<td align="center" class="tg-031e">80</td>
			<td align="center" class="tg-031e">120</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td class="tg-031e"><strong>hat</strong></td>
			<td align="center" class="tg-031e">160</td>
			<td align="center" class="tg-031e">90</td>
		</tr>
	</tbody>
</table>

<p> </p>
]]></question>
    <help/>
    <language><![CDATA[de]]></language>
    <script/>
   </row>
